{"tid":1306114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］五大訴求民間死線：714傍晚六時正 另招721反警暴遊行義工","createTime":"2019-07-11T04:50:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T10:39:55.000Z","uid":33736,"like":35,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"6d72267ae64eedd15b87ec9c4f26bcf124cb75aa","tid":1306114,"uid":33736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:50:47.000Z","msg":"呢幾日大家俾連儂牆、藍絲打人，光復呢啲議題Sidetrack得太耐，係時候回歸返重點。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求：</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撤回逃犯條例</span></span></strong><br />\n我哋唔係要壽終正寢，我哋要撤回。<br />\n重點唔係字眼，而係<strong>林鄭政府必須正視民意。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撤回612暴動定性</span></span></strong><br />\n林鄭回應嘅時候話佢冇定性話任何嘢。<br />\n我哋必須要求政府正名呢場抗爭<strong>並非暴動</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">必不追究反送中抗爭者</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong>手足們，我哋已經犧牲咗好多人，亦有好多義士被捕。</strong><br />\n一日唔撤銷控罪，唔承諾永不追究，我哋一日都仲活喺白色恐佈入面。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">成立獨立委員會調查警暴</span></span></strong><br />\n香港警隊已經偏離咗服務市民嘅宗旨，<br />\n成為咗<strong>一支不受控嘅武裝部隊。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">落實雙普選</span></span></strong><br />\n歸根究柢，大家都知道問題嘅根源係咩。<br />\n我哋必須要有一個<strong>由人民授權嘅政府、立法會</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n沙田嘅反送中遊行，係我哋俾政府嘅最後通諜。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n民間嘅死線已經定立：<br />\n7.14 1800</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，我諗住籌組反警暴大遊行，暫定721喺港島舉行。<br />\n以反警察暴力而唔係反送中嘅名義嘅原因，係因為當前對我哋抗爭最大嘅阻礙就係警察使用過份武力、情緒完全失控、公然違反警例行動，市民更毫無有效申訴渠道。<br />\n再唔處理呢個問題，每次嘅抗爭政權都可以用呢支失控嘅武裝部隊無所顧忌咁打壓。<br />\n<br />\n有興趣幫手、討論嘅朋友可以㩒入呢條link：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/K3H6uxcrPkRw__EhvS95cg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FK3H6uxcrPkRw__EhvS95cg&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt8521tf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=e838cfa0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/K3H6uxcrPkRw__EhvS95cg</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">7.21 唔理衝唔衝 都要出金鐘！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"ccec51117e04da74c048749e0deba753152d4a0d","tid":1306114,"uid":75040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:51:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b56e352c41b21f940a5ba2c9c2271ca898eac7c0","tid":1306114,"uid":33736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:55:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d7b3c5767c3cb5fa3a4133c28ee5a762311dc2e8","tid":1306114,"uid":75040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:58:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1c3a7ebb203d40ec32f29494030dea00de28552e","tid":1306114,"uid":268855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:58:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57f7d5aafd763f8a7e03cd318314278707b3f931","tid":1306114,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:58:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bdf867f8331c1c6d9ca19a8fc6bb7515fa807bff","tid":1306114,"uid":33736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:59:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f88e5748757ef3ea18836f7db539dc105d62f330","tid":1306114,"uid":122676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:00:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d19006b2cf1ffba212257e52ad8f90b0e415ddf9","tid":1306114,"uid":48667,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:00:29.000Z","msg":"重返港島戰線,對準政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個訴求都未回應呀屌<br />\n烈士依然死得不明不白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aad5b4a4766a3c4cccbb8ebfa9a66a58f9f4d0c","tid":1306114,"uid":59030,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:00:47.000Z","msg":"唔洗整deadline <br />\n佢都唔會理你<br />\n不合作運動填加佢管治成本&amp;搞到狗仔疲於奔命is ok"},{"pid":"365eeb8c7cc38126e42243d3cd62de71cb39787a","tid":1306114,"uid":59586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:01:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f18681fc4fae9f4a218a7a44a96faa9718945b32","tid":1306114,"uid":33736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d19006b2cf1ffba212257e52ad8f90b0e415ddf9","tid":1306114,"uid":48667,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:00:29.000Z","msg":"重返港島戰線,對準政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個訴求都未回應呀屌<br />\n烈士依然死得不明不白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:02:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"145482a506d99df60c1ed4c31f95b042d10c5728","tid":1306114,"uid":122676,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:02:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5c65ac4f8cc4da4c04c6d10b671591dce6a8c6e7","tid":1306114,"uid":122676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:03:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cf48236608858a9a9189e1070cee95483585e8e6","tid":1306114,"uid":59030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"145482a506d99df60c1ed4c31f95b042d10c5728","tid":1306114,"uid":122676,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9aad5b4a4766a3c4cccbb8ebfa9a66a58f9f4d0c","tid":1306114,"uid":59030,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:00:47.000Z","msg":"唔洗整deadline <br />\n佢都唔會理你<br />\n不合作運動填加佢管治成本&amp;搞到狗仔疲於奔命is ok"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:02:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:04:12.000Z","msg":"無視我地deadline<br />\n而我地又做唔到咩感覺有d柒"},{"pid":"8ed7cedcfb59788a9e22d56d94b1ece172854e80","tid":1306114,"uid":122676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:09:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7576974112bd82c52aaac384db2cf2ecd32aad0f","tid":1306114,"uid":260325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:11:23.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"7223b504fdb45da54d2b23f0fd40ccdfb96cf391","tid":1306114,"uid":263423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:13:48.000Z","msg":"終於！！！！"},{"pid":"36fe336801f82235316503d263657fa2b2ff7f2f","tid":1306114,"uid":263423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:14:17.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">上水個日大家要大力提沙田個日係死線</span></span><br />\n可派單派野<br />\n連番主線<br />\n令21號出師有名<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">集中討論：</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">集思講益講你想點</span><br />\n［極度認真］入嚟呀柒頭！講下一步可以點<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304173\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304173</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">暫時已有人提</span></span><br />\n <span style=\"color: green;\">活動主題：</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有曬日期內容差地點</span><br />\n而家做咩事?成場運動失晒焦 21號開警隊濫權大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304514\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304514</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">差日期有內容有地點</span><br />\n(置頂) 真普選抗爭三部曲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1303217\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1303217</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">死線建議：</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">令7月21名正言順</span><br />\n死線係沙田遊行 如無回應 7月21日全面升級 同我去金鐘<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1305585\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1305585</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">點宣傳活動：</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">學生同政府講有死線</span><br />\n（做實事）學生會唯一要傾個死線比政府<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304483\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304483</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">煲大比人打嘅事</span><br />\n[輿論反撲]多謝九龍灣後生仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1305553\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1305553</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">升級可以有嘅行動：</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大家唔好衝動呀和理呀<br />\n遊行跪地先係正路</span><br />\n&lt;集思廣益&gt; 行動第一波，點樣可以拆監控燈柱？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1300970\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1300970</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">同場加映：<br />\n助攻上水支線</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">課金送禮</span><br />\n[送到入更衣室] 地方的送禮勤需要你嘅支援<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1303150\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1303150</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span>"},{"pid":"e3c203b8827bcc06e89bbe0368d3defb41b456ce","tid":1306114,"uid":267277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9aad5b4a4766a3c4cccbb8ebfa9a66a58f9f4d0c","tid":1306114,"uid":59030,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:00:47.000Z","msg":"唔洗整deadline <br />\n佢都唔會理你<br />\n不合作運動填加佢管治成本&amp;搞到狗仔疲於奔命is ok"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:15:45.000Z","msg":"deadline 重要呀，對家唔理一回事，但所有人都會focus 呢個時間，可以令之後行動出師有名之外，仲可以凝聚到我地自己人"},{"pid":"c6b35f77b44762a05b07769e91ea7819bcbc6d19","tid":1306114,"uid":33736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3c203b8827bcc06e89bbe0368d3defb41b456ce","tid":1306114,"uid":267277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9aad5b4a4766a3c4cccbb8ebfa9a66a58f9f4d0c","tid":1306114,"uid":59030,"like